old enough for you.

43:25.209 --> 43:27.209
- It was my dad.
<i>- Really?</i>

43:27.918 --> 43:29.543
He's got a cop's face.

43:29.626 --> 43:30.793
<i>How do you know?</i>

43:32.626 --> 43:33.834
You have my wallet.

43:33.918 --> 43:35.001
<i>And your gun.</i>

43:35.084 --> 43:36.376
Think I can have 'em back?

43:36.459 --> 43:37.501
How do we do that?

43:37.584 --> 43:40.418
<i>Stop by my dad's place</i>
<i>and drop 'em off.</i>

43:40.543 --> 43:43.543
I'll give them to the SWAT
guy who answers the door.

43:43.668 --> 43:46.001
There's a guy here
on the task force right now.

43:46.084 --> 43:48.668
Maybe I should
put him on the phone.

43:48.751 --> 43:49.876
You wouldn't do that.

43:49.959 --> 43:51.084
Why not?

43:51.168 --> 43:52.876
You're having too much fun.

43:54.709 --> 43:56.834
She fixes him
pork chops and rice.

43:56.918 --> 43:59.501
Next thing you know, they're
making love on the sofa.

43:59.584 --> 44:01.334
She says he was very gentle.

44:01.418 --> 44:05.209
Chirino shows up at the house,
says he misses his little girl.

44:05.418 --> 44:09.001
She feels sorry for him.
Next thing you know, boom!

44:09.084 --> 44:10.501
On the couch.

44:10.584 --> 44:12.043
That's how you score now?

44:14.543 --> 44:15.668
I guess.

44:15.876 --> 44:18.084
There's something
I've been wondering.

44:18.168 --> 44:19.959
Whatever happened
to your uncle Cully?

44:20.376 --> 44:22.584
Think he's gonna
tell you where I am?

44:22.668 --> 44:23.834
<i>Unless you want to.</i>

44:23.918 --> 44:25.043
He's dead.

44:25.376 --> 44:27.376
Did 27 years before he got out,

44:27.459 --> 44:30.584
and he died a few years later
in a charity hospital

44:30.668 --> 44:33.084
<i>making up for all the</i>
<i>good times he missed.</i>

44:33.918 --> 44:35.626
That's not gonna be me.

44:35.709 --> 44:39.584
One last score, retire to some island?
Is that the idea?

44:40.793 --> 44:43.001
I'm partial to mountains myself,

44:43.084 --> 44:45.793
but if you like islands,
we'll make it an island.

44:45.876 --> 44:47.668
What do you mean, "we"?

44:47.751 --> 44:49.126
You and I can make it...

44:49.376 --> 44:50.501
You better see this.

44:50.584 --> 44:51.626
Is that Buddy?

44:51.709 --> 44:53.876
What? No. Okay. Bye-bye.

44:56.168 --> 44:57.918
So she's a married woman.

44:58.001 --> 45:00.751
But she goes to bed
with a prison escapee because

45:00.834 --> 45:03.418
he tells her that he
misses his little girl.

45:03.501 --> 45:06.501
She tells the world about it.
But you protect her.

45:06.626 --> 45:08.251
You don't reveal her name.

45:09.501 --> 45:12.251
That makes it sound like
what she was doing was okay

45:12.334 --> 45:14.793
as long as her husband
doesn't find out.

45:14.959 --> 45:16.459
Like a guy who cheats
on his wife.

45:16.543 --> 45:19.251
Says what she doesn't
know won't hurt her.

45:19.334 --> 45:20.709
Dad. What?

45:28.293 --> 45:31.418
Ray, I wanna show you
something in the living room.

45:33.959 --> 45:35.709
Good talking to you.

45:36.043 --> 45:37.084
You too.

45:40.793 --> 45:43.918
<i>NEWSCASTER: Federal law enforcement</i>
<i>agents raided a squatters camp</i>

45:44.001 --> 45:46.501
<i>north of Miami international</i>
<i>Airport this morning</i>

45:46.584 --> 45:51.084
<i>looking for fugitives from Tuesday's</i>
<i>escape from Glades Prison.</i>

45:51.751 --> 45:55.584
<i>F.B.I. officials confirm that one</i>
<i>of the escapees, Aurelio Linares,</i>

45:55.668 --> 45:56.668
<i>was killed...</i>

45:56.751 --> 45:58.126
JACK: Chino will want
to talk to me.

45:58.168 --> 46:01.626
China's runnin' for his life.
He don't give a shit about you.

46:01.709 --> 46:05.043
He'll know I gave him up.
He's gonna wanna find me.

46:05.126 --> 46:07.626
Maybe see Adele,
see what she knows.

46:08.584 --> 46:10.584
He knows where she lives?

46:13.959 --> 46:16.334
We were talking once,
drinking rum,

46:16.418 --> 46:19.168
and I may have mentioned Adele.

46:19.251 --> 46:21.751
How she worked for a magician.
He got all interested.

46:21.834 --> 46:24.209
He said, "How do you saw
the woman in half?"

46:24.293 --> 46:27.584
He wanted to meet her,
see her if she came to visit.

46:27.918 --> 46:31.543
So you call her up. Tell her
don't talk to any Cubans.

46:31.918 --> 46:33.751
The phone's probably tapped.

46:33.834 --> 46:34.834
You're right.

46:34.918 --> 46:37.043
Which means they have
her place staked out.

46:37.126 --> 46:38.251
Shit!

46:38.668 --> 46:40.043
[PHONE RINGING]

46:41.918 --> 46:43.501
Adele Delisi speaking.

46:44.168 --> 46:45.334
<i>CHINO: This is Adele?</i>

46:45.418 --> 46:46.584
Yes, it is.

46:47.293 --> 46:48.584
Sorry. Wrong number.

47:05.209 --> 47:06.418
Nice disguise.

47:08.584 --> 47:09.626
I'm a tourist.

47:11.168 --> 47:13.751
All right, here we go.

47:14.376 --> 47:17.376
Coming up right
here on the left.

47:18.251 --> 47:19.959
The guy with the clippers?

47:20.043 --> 47:21.668
I wonder what the F.B.I.

47:21.751 --> 47:24.168
is charging to trim
hedges these days?

47:24.251 --> 47:27.459
Quite a checker game
they got goin'.

47:27.543 --> 47:28.543
Pull on up.

47:51.751 --> 47:52.918
JACK: Oh, man.

48:03.334 --> 48:05.126
You saw her. That's all you get.

48:11.084 --> 48:12.668
Let's go to Detroit.

48:12.751 --> 48:14.334
Now you're talkin', brother.

48:16.001 --> 48:19.001
ADELE: I'll say one thing for
Jack, he's very considerate.

48:19.418 --> 48:21.126
Lights on or off, you know?

48:21.209 --> 48:22.293
Really?

48:26.376 --> 48:27.876
Adele, listen.

48:28.959 --> 48:33.418
I just want to find him before he does
something else and makes it worse.

48:35.959 --> 48:37.584
Buddy'll take care of him.

48:37.668 --> 48:40.918
Keep him out of trouble.
He's Jack's conscience.

48:42.418 --> 48:45.084
They must have robbed
fifty banks together.

48:45.251 --> 48:46.834
They were a really great team.

48:47.834 --> 48:48.918
Until they got busted.

48:49.834 --> 48:52.168
That wasn't Jack's fault.
That was on account of.

48:52.251 --> 48:56.834
Buddy. He decided to call his
sister and confess to the job

48:56.918 --> 48:59.084
before they'd done it
instead of after.

48:59.168 --> 49:02.918
