both ended up at Lompoc.

49:03.918 --> 49:06.751
I think Buddy felt
kind of bad about that.

49:08.126 --> 49:11.251
Do you have any idea
where I could find Buddy?

49:11.584 --> 49:12.793
Or Glenn?

49:12.876 --> 49:15.209
[KNOCKING]

49:15.293 --> 49:17.418
CHINO: Mira, Adele,
you in there?

49:17.918 --> 49:18.918
Yes.

49:18.959 --> 49:21.168
CHINO: Mira, I'd like
to speak to you.

49:21.584 --> 49:22.584
