you used to work for?

49:25.876 --> 49:28.418
He gave me your number
and where you live.

49:28.543 --> 49:31.293
I'm looking for an assistant.
Can I speak to you?

49:34.543 --> 49:36.209
You did work for Emile?

49:36.293 --> 49:39.459
I was Emile's box jumper
for four years.

49:39.918 --> 49:41.709
You were what? His box?

49:41.793 --> 49:43.293
His assistant.

49:45.584 --> 49:47.959
You say you perform
in the Miami area?

49:48.084 --> 49:50.293
CHINO: Here, there, you know.

49:50.918 --> 49:53.001
I was a magician in Cuba.

49:53.084 --> 49:54.709
They used to call me
Manuelito the Magician.

49:54.751 --> 49:56.418
<i>Mira</i>, can you please open?

49:56.918 --> 49:59.126
I'm not dressed.

49:59.209 --> 50:00.709
I'm a good friend of Jack Foley.

50:00.793 --> 50:01.876
CHINO: You know Jack?

50:01.959 --> 50:03.001
Who are you?

50:04.334 --> 50:05.751
CHINO: Jose Chirino.

50:06.543 --> 50:10.001
Maybe you heard Jack call me Chino.
I'm the same guy.

50:10.709 --> 50:13.709
Tell him to wait in the hall.
You have to get dressed.

50:13.834 --> 50:16.084
Wait in the hall.
You have to get dressed.

50:16.168 --> 50:19.876
Tell me where to find Jack and
I don't bother you no more.

50:19.959 --> 50:21.168
Come on, please!

50:22.251 --> 50:23.459
I don't know where he is.

50:23.543 --> 50:25.418
I helped Jack escape.

50:25.918 --> 50:27.668
CHINO: Open this fucking door...

50:27.751 --> 50:29.334
I'm gonna call the police.

50:29.751 --> 50:33.709
CHINO: Why you gonna do that
to a friend of Jack?

50:37.168 --> 50:38.501
