50:45.751 --> 50:47.751
[CHINO GROANING]

50:49.626 --> 50:51.668
Adele! Give me your hand.

50:52.584 --> 50:54.543
You not Adele! I'm a U.S. marshal
and you're under arrest.

50:54.584 --> 50:55.918
Get my bag, Adele.

50:57.793 --> 51:00.334
I think there's
a misunderstanding.

51:00.418 --> 51:01.543
You got nice bag.

51:01.626 --> 51:04.834
Let's say we just forget about it.
I go home...

51:04.918 --> 51:06.751
Shut up.

51:06.834 --> 51:08.001
Who the hell taught
you how to do that?

51:08.043 --> 51:09.043
Give me your other hand.

51:09.126 --> 51:10.376
Okay.

51:10.834 --> 51:12.126
[CHINO GROANS]

51:12.209 --> 51:13.584
I gotta go make pee-pee.

51:17.376 --> 51:18.834
You are mean!

51:19.293 --> 51:23.584
I'm gonna call my lawyer. This
is human rights violation.

51:24.668 --> 51:26.584
Daniel Burdon, please.
Karen Sisco.

51:27.959 --> 51:29.959
Can I ask you a question?

51:30.043 --> 51:32.043
You know that trick you do?

51:32.126 --> 51:35.584
Karen? Where are you? I've
been trying to reach you.

51:35.668 --> 51:37.918
When you're in the box
and they saw you in half?

51:38.168 --> 51:39.501
I'm at Adele Delisi's.

51:39.584 --> 51:40.668
It's magic.

51:41.084 --> 51:44.043
We already talked to her.
That's a dead end.

51:44.126 --> 51:48.168
If I bring in Chirino, will
you put me on the task force?

51:48.251 --> 51:49.543
DANIEL: Sure.

51:49.626 --> 51:51.834
They put the saw through,
and separate it.

51:51.918 --> 51:54.418
But how do you
twinkle your toes?

51:54.626 --> 51:57.793
You bring Chirino in, and you
can be on the task force.

51:57.918 --> 52:00.001
That's all I wanted to know.

52:00.959 --> 52:03.501
Now, forget about the ex-wife,

52:03.834 --> 52:06.251
and get over to the Adams Hotel?

52:07.084 --> 52:08.459
You got it.

52:09.293 --> 52:10.376
No!

52:12.751 --> 52:14.668
That's it.

52:14.751 --> 52:15.751
Fake legs.

52:17.251 --> 52:19.376
Fake legs? How you gonna...

52:20.584 --> 52:21.668
Thanks, Adele.

52:21.751 --> 52:23.834
CHINO: How do they twinkle
their toes, if it's fake?

52:27.084 --> 52:29.751
First thing we do in
Detroit, we find Glenn,

52:29.876 --> 52:32.751
and we find a window
to throw him out of.

52:33.043 --> 52:34.959
I was thinkin', if I was Glenn

52:35.043 --> 52:37.084
taking down the Ripper,
where would I go?

52:37.209 --> 52:40.084
Except if you were Glenn,
you wouldn't be thinkin'.

52:40.209 --> 52:42.418
Remember Snoopy Miller,
his pal from the joint?

52:42.543 --> 52:45.168
I figured he'd be
brain-dead by now.

52:45.251 --> 52:47.251
Snoop doesn't box anymore.

52:47.376 --> 52:50.584
Glenn told me that he manages
some fighters at the Kronk.

53:05.084 --> 53:06.293
Did you get the key?

53:06.376 --> 53:07.626
They're in Room 613.

53:11.418 --> 53:14.251
I want two men outside,
front and back.

53:14.918 --> 53:18.918
Conroy, Jameson, go on up to six.
Cover both ends of the hall.

53:20.084 --> 53:22.793
You're primary.
You're secondary.

53:22.959 --> 53:24.168
You're point man.

53:25.543 --> 53:26.834
You gonna use a ram?

53:26.918 --> 53:28.918
Yeah. Why?

53:29.168 --> 53:31.001
The manager's door is metal.

53:31.084 --> 53:32.668
They might all be.

53:33.876 --> 53:36.751
A ram on a metal door makes a
lot of noise and that's it.

53:36.834 --> 53:39.626
I have a shock lock
round on my shotgun.

53:39.709 --> 53:41.751
Fine. Whatever.

53:52.334 --> 53:53.751
Two, please.

53:56.584 --> 53:57.626
Two.

53:58.376 --> 53:59.376
<i>[CLEARS THROAT]</i>

54:02.543 --> 54:04.418
Let's take the stairs.

54:07.293 --> 54:10.418
Take the radio. Stay here in the
lobby and watch the elevator.

54:10.501 --> 54:12.084
Daniel, I want to go upstairs.

54:12.168 --> 54:14.709
You can wait in the car
if you want to.

54:15.584 --> 54:19.001
You see Foley and Bragg coming behind us.
What do you do?

54:19.084 --> 54:20.584
Call and tell you?

54:20.668 --> 54:22.668
And let them come up.

54:22.918 --> 54:26.251
Don't try to make the bust yourself.
You understand?

54:32.334 --> 54:34.376
Is this your floor, ma'am?

54:35.959 --> 54:37.668
Is this your floor, ma'am?

54:37.751 --> 54:40.584
On! [CHUCKLES] Oh, yes.

54:40.709 --> 54:43.126
It is. I'm sorry. Thank you.

54:47.459 --> 54:50.251
Be advised we are
approaching the door.

54:59.293 --> 55:02.168
Be advised we are
going to blow the door.

55:06.501 --> 55:07.501
[FIRING]

55:08.209 --> 55:09.209
[ELEVATOR BELL DINGS]

55:12.251 --> 55:13.418
Going up?

