I thought I was going up.

55:33.668 --> 55:35.834
She just looked right at me.

55:36.418 --> 55:38.251
Who? Karen.

55:39.751 --> 55:41.584
Karen Sisco? Yeah.

55:43.293 --> 55:45.001
She's in the lobby.

55:45.751 --> 55:47.043
She's in the lobby? Yeah.

55:48.584 --> 55:52.251
If they know where I live, they know
what I drive. We got to dump this car.

56:01.168 --> 56:04.043
She just sat there,
looking right at me.

56:08.459 --> 56:12.001
DANIEL: <i>They're not up here.</i>
<i>Keep your eyes open.</i>

56:13.084 --> 56:16.418
<i>Karen, are you there?</i>

56:17.168 --> 56:18.251
<i>MARSHALL: He waved at you?</i>

56:18.918 --> 56:20.876
I'm pretty sure he did.

56:20.959 --> 56:22.168
Did you wave back?

56:22.251 --> 56:23.334
I didn't have time.

56:23.418 --> 56:25.584
I imagine you
would have, though.

56:26.959 --> 56:28.668
Buddy's sister,
Regina Mary Bragg,

56:28.751 --> 56:31.168
got two calls from Buddy
in Detroit this morning.

56:31.251 --> 56:32.959
She calls Burdon.

56:33.043 --> 56:34.543
He got Buddy's address
from her, too.

56:34.626 --> 56:35.751
So?

56:36.084 --> 56:39.251
Why does he still call her
after she turned him in?

56:39.376 --> 56:41.209
He doesn't hold a grudge.

56:41.543 --> 56:43.834
But if they have
this big score up north,

56:43.918 --> 56:46.168
why did Foley stay
in Miami for so long?

56:46.251 --> 56:47.709
Any thoughts on that?

56:47.793 --> 56:49.251
None I'd like to share.

56:50.334 --> 56:51.668
I'll call you when I get in.

56:51.751 --> 56:52.834
Okay.

57:23.251 --> 57:26.084
MAURICE: I don't just deal product
and manage fighters no more.

57:27.376 --> 57:30.626
