myself, you know, diversified.

57:34.209 --> 57:36.334
I'm into the occasional
grand larceny,

57:36.418 --> 57:38.668
home invasion, shit like that.

57:38.751 --> 57:40.834
White Boy Bob here
is my all-around man.

57:40.918 --> 57:44.168
