58:02.168 --> 58:03.459
Ain't gonna have
no police on our ass,

58:03.501 --> 58:04.959
nothing like that.
It's nice, man.

58:08.084 --> 58:11.584
You still haven't said how
you want to do this thing.

58:11.668 --> 58:15.418
I'll tell you once we get
one other brother I need.

58:16.168 --> 58:18.209
Kenneth,
that's Moselle's brother,

58:18.293 --> 58:20.334
along with White Boy here.

58:22.043 --> 58:23.126
Here we go, White Boy.

58:26.876 --> 58:28.459
[HONKING]

58:33.168 --> 58:34.834
Who's the fireman?

58:37.626 --> 58:38.834
Ken Dog.

58:40.626 --> 58:41.918
What's up?

58:42.001 --> 58:43.376
MAURICE: What's happenin',
hustler?

58:45.751 --> 58:47.418
This cigarette gonna bother you?

58:47.501 --> 58:51.251
Put that thing out.
Ken, this is Glenn.

58:51.334 --> 58:54.418
Glenn, that's Kenny, the dude
I was tellin' you about.

58:55.084 --> 58:58.001
You're the one gonna help us
rip off that rich white dude?

58:58.293 --> 58:59.459
That's him.

58:59.543 --> 59:00.626
Help you?

59:01.668 --> 59:02.793
Go ahead, White Boy.

59:12.043 --> 59:16.918
Maurice, I am letting you
in on this gig, not...

59:19.126 --> 59:21.501
You just asked
how we gonna do it.

59:21.584 --> 59:24.209
I'm telling you how.
We're the experts.

59:25.334 --> 59:27.084
The one I'm worried
about is you, Glenn.

59:28.168 --> 59:29.209
Me?

59:29.918 --> 59:31.709
Can you step up
and actually do this shit

59:31.793 --> 59:33.584
instead of just
talking the talk?

59:35.084 --> 59:36.293
Do what?

59:37.251 --> 59:39.543
Walk into a house I picked out.

59:39.626 --> 59:42.168
Do this cross-dressing nigger
I used to sell to.

59:42.251 --> 59:44.043
Been dealing on his own.

59:44.126 --> 59:45.918
What? When?

