another one.

01:00:28.376 --> 01:00:30.084
If I say we in
on this Ripley shit,

01:00:30.168 --> 01:00:32.001
we in on it,
with or without you.

01:00:32.084 --> 01:00:34.501
If I say you do
this motherfucker

01:00:34.584 --> 01:00:36.751
to show me you got balls,

01:00:36.876 --> 01:00:38.834
guess what else you gonna do?

01:00:39.418 --> 01:00:40.834
WHITE BOY: We're here.

