01:33:35.168 --> 01:33:36.834
You got two minutes.

01:33:36.918 --> 01:33:38.293
Make up your mind.

01:33:38.376 --> 01:33:39.709
I wasn't asking permission.

01:33:49.501 --> 01:33:50.834
You know they're
gonna set us up.

01:33:50.918 --> 01:33:52.626
I get that feeling.

01:33:52.709 --> 01:33:55.334
You think you can get to the
diamonds before they do?

01:33:57.293 --> 01:34:00.959
I'll make you a deal.
You get outta here right now.

01:34:01.043 --> 01:34:04.543
I'll do the job with Snoop,
meet you, give you half.

01:34:05.084 --> 01:34:06.459
Half for doin' what?

01:34:06.543 --> 01:34:08.293
Gettin' me out of Glades,
for starters.

01:34:09.501 --> 01:34:11.084
Who's gonna watch your back?

01:35:55.334 --> 01:35:56.751
All right, White Boy.
House call.

01:36:15.334 --> 01:36:16.793
[DOORBELL RINGING]

01:36:20.043 --> 01:36:21.043
Ready to do this?

01:36:21.084 --> 01:36:22.293
Ready for whatever.

01:36:22.376 --> 01:36:24.418
Cool. My shit always work.

01:36:26.584 --> 01:36:28.334
WHITE BOY: Perennial Plumbing.

01:36:30.751 --> 01:36:32.293
WHITE BOY: Somebody called.

01:36:33.459 --> 01:36:37.209
You don't know what you're talking
about, because no one was here.

01:36:37.418 --> 01:36:38.793
Let's go skiing.

01:36:42.918 --> 01:36:44.918
JACK: You still got time
to take me up on my offer.

01:36:45.001 --> 01:36:46.834
BUDDY: And leave you alone
with these assholes?

01:36:49.959 --> 01:36:51.376
<i>Raymond Cruz.</i>

01:36:51.459 --> 01:36:53.793
It's Karen Sisco.
I'm at Ripley's house.

01:36:53.876 --> 01:36:57.001
Maurice Miller and four other
men just forced their way in.

01:36:57.084 --> 01:36:58.793
They're armed.
I'm gonna need backup.

01:36:58.959 --> 01:37:00.959
Who are you? MIDGE: I work here.

01:37:01.043 --> 01:37:03.126
I'm the maid. Fuck off!

01:37:03.209 --> 01:37:06.501
That's exactly what I'm gonna
do, fuck you, then off you.

01:37:07.001 --> 01:37:08.001
Where Ripley at?

01:37:08.084 --> 01:37:09.334
He isn't here.

01:37:10.001 --> 01:37:11.668
Out for the evening
or some shit?

01:37:11.751 --> 01:37:13.668
He's in Florida, Palm Beach.

01:37:15.626 --> 01:37:16.876
When's he due back?

01:37:16.959 --> 01:37:18.584
You gonna wait for him?

01:37:19.459 --> 01:37:22.918
Mr. Ripley's down for the season.
Christmas to Easter.

01:37:23.459 --> 01:37:24.959
Stop that shit.

01:37:26.168 --> 01:37:28.293
You're here all by yourself?

01:37:28.418 --> 01:37:30.626
That's right. Just me.

01:37:36.251 --> 01:37:38.751
Where's Ripley's safe,
his valuables?

01:37:38.834 --> 01:37:40.043
I don't have any idea.

01:37:40.126 --> 01:37:42.084
I fuckin' bet you don't.

01:37:42.918 --> 01:37:46.168
We gonna take a look upstairs
in the man's bedroom.

01:37:46.584 --> 01:37:49.293
You and Mr. Buddy look
at all the rooms down here.

01:37:49.418 --> 01:37:52.709
Check the paintings,
behind the walls.

01:37:52.793 --> 01:37:54.918
The man's got a safe.
It's here somewhere.

01:37:55.001 --> 01:37:56.918
What about his place
down in Florida?

01:37:57.001 --> 01:37:58.501
If you'd called,
we could have checked

01:37:58.584 --> 01:38:00.376
the walls down there
before we left.

01:38:00.459 --> 01:38:03.584
That is, if you'd bothered
to find out where he was.

01:38:05.293 --> 01:38:07.293
Take this bitch upstairs.

01:38:12.918 --> 01:38:15.751
You try and trip any alarms,
anything like that,

01:38:15.876 --> 01:38:17.834
you gonna be a dead hazel,
you understand me?

01:38:21.376 --> 01:38:22.626
Where we at? Where is it?

01:38:22.709 --> 01:38:23.709
Over there.

01:38:23.793 --> 01:38:25.834
Ever wear one of these?

01:38:25.918 --> 01:38:26.918
I don't ski.

01:38:27.418 --> 01:38:30.584
Keep an eye on the maid.
I'll have a look around.

01:38:35.418 --> 01:38:38.334
Go sit down. Please.

01:38:42.751 --> 01:38:46.751
Damn, Mo. How's this
motherfucker livin'?

01:38:49.209 --> 01:38:50.876
Check behind the pictures
on the walls.

01:38:54.543 --> 01:38:56.543
Hey, Mo. Found some rubbers.

01:38:57.001 --> 01:38:59.751
White Boy, why the fuck you
lookin' under the mattress?

01:38:59.834 --> 01:39:02.501
You know dude ain't gonna
hide no diamonds under there.

01:39:02.584 --> 01:39:04.834
Damn! Dumb Alabama motherfucker.

01:39:04.918 --> 01:39:06.918
Where Foley?

01:39:07.001 --> 01:39:08.959
Checkin' the other rooms
like you said.

01:39:12.293 --> 01:39:13.543
Keep an eye on Foley.

01:39:20.459 --> 01:39:22.251
[STATIC ON RADIO]

01:39:23.043 --> 01:39:25.209
MAURICE: Ken, stop fuckin'
with the radio, put on a CD.

01:39:26.543 --> 01:39:28.168
I don't recognize
none of these bands, Mo.

01:39:28.209 --> 01:39:29.418
Just pick somebody.

01:39:30.168 --> 01:39:31.709
What, "How to Sing
like Michael Bolton"?

01:39:35.668 --> 01:39:37.459
What the fuck you
wanna listen to?

01:39:38.293 --> 01:39:40.626
I like Schubert.

01:39:40.709 --> 01:39:42.751
Schubert? Well, I don't.

01:39:48.626 --> 01:39:49.626
Foley?

01:39:54.209 --> 01:39:55.209
[CLATTERING]

01:39:58.668 --> 01:39:59.751
Cool.

01:41:01.209 --> 01:41:03.126
911 got you on hold, Richard?

01:41:04.584 --> 01:41:06.418
Foley! How you doin'?

01:41:06.584 --> 01:41:08.751
What in God's name
is happening here?

01:41:08.834 --> 01:41:09.959
Who's upstairs?

01:41:10.043 --> 01:41:11.668
Snoopy Miller,
couple of his friends.

01:41:11.751 --> 01:41:14.168
Maurice, from Lompoc?

01:41:15.001 --> 01:41:16.751
Have they got Midge up there?

01:41:16.834 --> 01:41:19.459
What man lets a woman
answer the door this late?

01:41:19.584 --> 01:41:23.168
We thought it was her husband. He
comes here and checks up on her.

01:41:23.251 --> 01:41:25.209
I'm supposed to
be down in Florida.

01:41:25.293 --> 01:41:27.668
In a few minutes, you'll wish you were.
Let's go. Come on.

01:41:27.751 --> 01:41:29.959
Sit down.
We'll look at your fish.

01:41:34.043 --> 01:41:36.376
That's workin'. That's workin'.

01:41:42.001 --> 01:41:43.418
[GASPS]

01:41:44.376 --> 01:41:46.709
Motherfucker! I found the safe!

01:41:49.126 --> 01:41:50.751
Don't go nowhere.

01:41:54.418 --> 01:41:56.293
Shit! We gonna have a party!

01:41:56.376 --> 01:41:57.668
Look at that bitch.

01:42:10.751 --> 01:42:11.876
They found the safe.

01:42:11.959 --> 01:42:13.418
Fuck.

01:42:13.501 --> 01:42:14.834
Buddy, you remember Richard?

01:42:14.918 --> 01:42:16.459
Hi. Nice house.

01:42:16.543 --> 01:42:17.626
Thank you.

01:42:20.501 --> 01:42:22.668
We just all hit this handle,

01:42:22.751 --> 01:42:24.751
blow this sucker wide open.

01:42:26.918 --> 01:42:28.209
Let's get ready.

01:42:28.293 --> 01:42:29.834
You're gonna kill me with that.

01:42:33.959 --> 01:42:35.001
Where you been, man?

01:42:35.084 --> 01:42:36.626
Found some steaks.

01:42:36.709 --> 01:42:37.709
Steaks?

01:42:37.793 --> 01:42:38.793
Some big ones, bro.

01:42:40.084 --> 01:42:42.251
Come on,
blast this damn safe open.

01:42:42.334 --> 01:42:43.918
He's down there
lookin' for food.

01:42:44.001 --> 01:42:45.084
Fool.

01:42:47.251 --> 01:42:49.209
Hold it. No.
Get to the side, man.

01:42:51.584 --> 01:42:54.959
On three. One, two, three.

01:42:57.668 --> 01:42:59.501
Jesus, they're shooting Midge!

01:42:59.584 --> 01:43:00.626
Sit down, Dick.

01:43:00.709 --> 01:43:02.668
They're trying to open up
the safe, not your maid.

01:43:02.918 --> 01:43:04.584
[LAUGHING]

01:43:05.334 --> 01:43:06.459
KENNETH: Shit.

01:43:07.918 --> 01:43:09.293
We didn't even crack it.

01:43:20.459 --> 01:43:22.001
Hit the hinges.

01:43:22.626 --> 01:43:25.418
Put your finger in your ear, man.
This is gonna be loud.

01:43:25.501 --> 01:43:28.376
On three. One, two...

01:43:28.459 --> 01:43:33.001
The combination is 3-10-44.

01:43:36.293 --> 01:43:37.793
Richard's birthday.

01:43:37.876 --> 01:43:38.918
Thank you.

01:43:59.126 --> 01:44:00.626
Are they dead?

01:44:03.418 --> 01:44:04.501
We gotta find Foley.

01:44:04.584 --> 01:44:07.584
Can't believe you're still angry
with me after all this time.

01:44:07.709 --> 01:44:10.876
I'm not angry with you. In
fact, I'm completely relaxed.

01:44:10.959 --> 01:44:15.209
I can't figure if it's the
fish that are cooling me out,

01:44:15.293 --> 01:44:19.084
or all those uncut diamonds in
the bottom of the tank, there.

01:44:26.251 --> 01:44:27.501
Goddamn.

01:44:27.876 --> 01:44:30.501
Glenn was right. You got about
5 million worth in there?

01:44:30.584 --> 01:44:32.168
Five point two.

01:44:34.584 --> 01:44:36.584
They just look
like plain ol' rocks!

01:44:36.709 --> 01:44:39.209
They sure do.
You wanna grab 'em?

01:44:45.751 --> 01:44:49.084
If I were you,
I'd get up and run.

01:44:49.501 --> 01:44:50.876
I'm not leaving Midge.

01:44:50.959 --> 01:44:52.334
They're gonna kill you.

01:44:52.418 --> 01:44:54.126
If that's my fate then so be it.

01:44:54.209 --> 01:44:56.918
I won't leave her.
I'm in love with her.

01:44:59.251 --> 01:45:00.251
Come on, Jack.

01:45:01.168 --> 01:45:02.209
Good luck, Richard.

01:45:19.334 --> 01:45:20.793
Come on, Jack.

01:45:20.876 --> 01:45:22.959
They're gonna rape
that maid, aren't they?

01:45:23.043 --> 01:45:25.293
By the look of those guys,
the Ripper too.

01:45:25.376 --> 01:45:27.251
Then they're gonna kill 'em.
At least.

01:45:32.209 --> 01:45:33.334
Tricky motherfucker.

01:45:33.418 --> 01:45:34.501
Are those my suits?

01:45:34.584 --> 01:45:38.584
These are my suits. Look at you.

01:45:40.126 --> 01:45:41.334
Where you been hidin', Dick?

01:45:43.918 --> 01:45:45.168
We made it, didn't we?

01:45:45.251 --> 01:45:46.918
Just get in the van.

01:45:47.001 --> 01:45:48.043
<i>I'm going back in.</i>

01:45:48.751 --> 01:45:50.043
I'm goin' with you.

01:45:50.126 --> 01:45:51.543
Meet me at the airport.

01:45:51.626 --> 01:45:53.501
I'll get one of Ripley's cars.

01:45:53.584 --> 01:45:54.834
The shit about to go down here,

01:45:54.918 --> 01:45:57.751
you'll be on the phone
with your sister for a month.

01:45:58.459 --> 01:45:59.918
I'm sayin' we're square.

01:46:01.168 --> 01:46:02.334
Here.

01:46:14.793 --> 01:46:16.126
Get out of here!

01:46:36.043 --> 01:46:37.043
Get that shit off.

01:46:37.084 --> 01:46:38.168
Get your hands off me!

01:46:38.251 --> 01:46:40.209
Shut up!
Nobody's gonna help you.

01:46:43.918 --> 01:46:46.751
Fuck Midge.
Where the jewels at, Dick?

01:46:46.834 --> 01:46:49.126
Foley's got them.

01:46:49.209 --> 01:46:50.418
Where the fuck is Foley?

01:46:57.001 --> 01:46:58.001
Midge.

01:46:58.084 --> 01:47:00.084
[GUN FIRING]

01:47:05.418 --> 01:47:06.459
Midge!

01:47:06.543 --> 01:47:07.751
Sit your punk ass down.

01:47:08.793 --> 01:47:10.251
[GROANS]

01:47:10.918 --> 01:47:12.043
Son of a bitch!

01:47:13.001 --> 01:47:14.834
Take the front stairs.
I'm gonna take the back.

01:47:18.251 --> 01:47:19.334
You all right?

01:47:19.418 --> 01:47:20.418
Where's Richard?

01:47:20.709 --> 01:47:23.751
He's downstairs. You wait here.

01:47:29.376 --> 01:47:32.834
Hold it, asshole. Drop the gun.

01:47:36.626 --> 01:47:38.668
Put the damn gun down, now.

01:47:42.126 --> 01:47:43.543
[SHOUTING] Put it down!

01:47:48.668 --> 01:47:51.709
Stay right there.
Don't move. Maurice!

01:47:52.168 --> 01:47:53.543
I got Foley!

01:47:57.001 --> 01:47:58.084
Maurice!

01:48:14.584 --> 01:48:15.626
[GUN FIRES]

01:48:22.418 --> 01:48:23.418
[GUN CLICKS]

01:48:29.793 --> 01:48:31.793
Ain't got another clip
I can use, do you?

01:48:31.876 --> 01:48:33.293
No, I don't.

01:48:36.209 --> 01:48:38.501
Never shot a gun before,
have you?

01:48:38.584 --> 01:48:40.126
Not until recently, no.

01:48:40.418 --> 01:48:41.501
You a little nervous?

01:48:41.584 --> 01:48:42.918
Little bit.

01:48:43.043 --> 01:48:47.293
A situation like this
has a high potentiality

01:48:47.376 --> 01:48:49.001
for the common
motherfucker to bitch out.

01:48:49.084 --> 01:48:50.751
So I figure, why take a chance?

01:48:53.918 --> 01:48:55.084
Bitch!

01:48:59.543 --> 01:49:00.709
Motherfucker!

01:49:36.001 --> 01:49:37.584
Stop! Put your hands in the air!

01:49:46.043 --> 01:49:47.043
[EXCLAIMING]

01:49:54.334 --> 01:49:55.334
KAREN: Jack!

01:49:57.709 --> 01:49:59.584
KAREN: I know you're up there.

01:49:59.668 --> 01:50:00.709
Shit!

01:50:03.084 --> 01:50:05.959
KAREN: Where's Kenneth?

01:50:06.043 --> 01:50:07.084
He's up here.

01:50:09.084 --> 01:50:10.418
He's dead.

01:50:33.084 --> 01:50:34.834
Come on, Jack, don't.

01:50:34.918 --> 01:50:36.084
Pretend it's not me.

01:50:36.251 --> 01:50:38.001
You think I'd shoot you?

01:50:38.084 --> 01:50:39.834
If you don't,
somebody else will.

01:50:39.918 --> 01:50:41.918
What're you now? A desperado?

01:50:43.334 --> 01:50:46.084
Put the gun down.

01:50:46.168 --> 01:50:47.251
I'm not goin' back.

01:50:49.418 --> 01:50:53.584
Don't make me do this.
Put the gun down.

01:50:57.876 --> 01:51:00.168
Damn it, Jack, put the gun down!

01:51:00.251 --> 01:51:01.626
[SIRENS WAILING]

01:51:02.209 --> 01:51:03.876
No more time-outs.

01:51:13.793 --> 01:51:15.293
You win, Jack.

01:51:18.126 --> 01:51:19.668
[GROANING]

01:51:24.084 --> 01:51:25.543
I can't shoot you.

01:51:25.626 --> 01:51:27.668
You did. You shot me.

01:51:27.751 --> 01:51:29.043
You know what I mean.

01:51:43.751 --> 01:51:47.751
I'm sorry. I wish
things were different.

01:52:30.918 --> 01:52:32.084
Airport.

01:52:59.834 --> 01:53:03.501
<i>KAREN: They don't know yet if they</i>
<i>want to bring him up on the homicides.</i>

01:53:03.584 --> 01:53:06.584
<i>I doubt if they will. They'll</i>
<i>just put a detainer on him.</i>

01:53:06.709 --> 01:53:09.668
<i>When they're through with him</i>
<i>here, he'll go back to Florida.</i>

01:53:09.751 --> 01:53:11.834
<i>MARSHALL: Are you</i>
<i>gonna go get him?</i>

01:53:11.918 --> 01:53:13.751
<i>KAREN: It's possible. Why?</i>

01:53:14.376 --> 01:53:15.668
<i>MARSHALL: I was just thinking.</i>

01:53:15.751 --> 01:53:18.251
<i>You can have a nice time</i>
<i>with him on the ride down,</i>

01:53:18.376 --> 01:53:21.376
<i>picking up where your</i>
<i>"interlude" left off,</i>

01:53:21.709 --> 01:53:24.584
<i>then you can throw him</i>
<i>in the shithouse.</i>

01:53:25.793 --> 01:53:27.918
KAREN: <i>He knew</i>
<i>what he was doing.</i>

01:53:28.043 --> 01:53:30.418
<i>Nobody forced him to rob banks.</i>

01:53:32.251 --> 01:53:35.084
<i>MARSHALL: My little girl.</i>
<i>The tough babe.</i>

01:53:36.876 --> 01:53:38.626
<i>KAREN: I'll call you later.</i>

01:53:38.751 --> 01:53:40.084
<i>MARSHALL: Good-bye.</i>

01:53:57.918 --> 01:53:58.918
KAREN: Jack.

01:54:03.168 --> 01:54:04.918
I got you a present.

01:54:07.918 --> 01:54:09.293
Something for the road.

01:54:21.709 --> 01:54:23.668
I'm gonna have
to take it away, though,

01:54:23.751 --> 01:54:25.876
soon as the ride is over.

01:54:38.459 --> 01:54:40.793
OFFICER: Jack Foley?
Meet Hejira Henry.

01:54:52.751 --> 01:54:54.376
What kind of a name is Hejira?

01:54:54.459 --> 01:54:55.709
It's Islamic.

01:54:55.793 --> 01:54:57.043
What's it stand for?

01:54:57.709 --> 01:55:01.209
The "Hejira" was Muhammad's
flight from Mecca in 622.

01:55:01.501 --> 01:55:02.751
His flight?

01:55:03.334 --> 01:55:06.251
Brothers in Leavenworth
gave me that name.

01:55:06.584 --> 01:55:08.043
You were in Leavenworth?

01:55:08.126 --> 01:55:09.918
For a time. Meaning?

01:55:10.626 --> 01:55:12.793
Meaning, the time came, I left.

01:55:12.876 --> 01:55:13.918
You busted out.

01:55:14.251 --> 01:55:18.334
I prefer to think of it as an
exodus from an undesirable place.

01:55:20.543 --> 01:55:22.334
How long before you got caught?

01:55:22.418 --> 01:55:23.543
That time?

01:55:25.293 --> 01:55:26.418
There were others?

01:55:26.501 --> 01:55:28.418
That was the ninth.

01:55:30.543 --> 01:55:31.876
The ninth?

01:55:33.584 --> 01:55:37.334
Ten if you count that prison
hospital I walked away from.

01:55:37.501 --> 01:55:38.668
You done a lot
of walkin', Henry.

01:55:38.709 --> 01:55:39.793
Hejira.

01:55:39.918 --> 01:55:43.459
Hejira. Now we're off to Glades.

01:55:44.834 --> 01:55:46.501
It looks that way.

01:55:47.334 --> 01:55:50.709
I was supposed to leave last
night with the lady marshal.

01:55:50.793 --> 01:55:53.418
For some reason
she wanted to wait.

01:55:53.834 --> 01:55:54.918
JACK: She did?

01:55:55.001 --> 01:55:57.251
Guess it's cheaper
taking us in one van.

01:55:58.418 --> 01:56:02.918
Could be. Maybe she thought
we had a lot to talk about.

01:56:03.459 --> 01:56:05.126
Really? Like what?

01:56:06.626 --> 01:56:10.418
I don't know.
Long ride to Florida.
